<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="id77c50c8e-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5" identifier="/us/usc/t16/s460n–9"><num value="460n–9">§ 460n–9.</num><heading> Authorization of appropriations</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are hereby authorized to be appropriated not more than $7,100,000 for the acquisition of land and interests in land pursuant to <ref href="/us/usc/t16/s460n–1">section 460n–1 of this title</ref>.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="id77c50c8f-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5">(<ref href="/us/pl/88/639/s10">Pub. L. 88–639, § 10</ref>, <date date="1964-10-08">Oct. 8, 1964</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/78/1041">78 Stat. 1041</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/93/477/tI/s101/12">Pub. L. 93–477, title I, § 101(12)</ref>, <date date="1974-10-26">Oct. 26, 1974</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/88/1445">88 Stat. 1445</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
