<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="id77c50c91-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="id77c50c92-6992-11f1-ab3f-8b4c043f8cd5"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">1974—<ref href="/us/pl/93/477">Pub. L. 93–477</ref> substituted “$7,100,000” for “$1,200,000”.</p>
</note>
